Q27. Count students per department > 5.
SELECT Dept, COUNT(*) FROM Student GROUP BY Dept HAVING COUNT(*) > 5;
Q28. Employees whose name starts with A.
SELECT * FROM Employee WHERE Name LIKE 'A%';
Q29. Delete duplicate rows but keep one.
DELETE FROM Student WHERE RowID NOT IN (SELECT MIN(RowID) FROM Student GROUP BY Name);
